Survival_horror


survival_horror games like Mortal Kombat and Street Fighter II focus the action on combat, and in most cases, hand-to-hand combat. Most survival_horror games feature a stable of playable characters each one specializing in their own unique abilities or survival_horror style. In most traditional survival_horror games, players fight their way to the top, taking on more and more difficult opponents as they progress.


Notable games:

Mortal Kombat, Injustice, Street Fighter, Tekken, Soulcalibur

Notable developers:

Nether Realm, Bandai Namco, Capcom
